<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en-US" dir="ltr" data-bs-theme="dark">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <meta name="description" content="Global farming minigame statistics and leaderboards for IsekaiExpress.">
  <title>Farm stats · IsekaiExpress</title>
  <link rel="shortcut icon" type="image/x-icon" href="/public/assets/img/favicons/favicon.ico">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=DM+Sans:ital,opsz,wght@0,9..40,400;0,9..40,500;0,9..40,600;0,9..40,700;1,9..40,400&family=Instrument+Serif:ital@0;1&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link href="/public/assets/css/theme.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <link href="/public/assets/css/custom.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    :root {
      --farm-bg: #0c0f12;
      --farm-surface: #141a21;
      --farm-border: rgba(120, 200, 150, 0.12);
      --farm-accent: #6ecf8e;
      --farm-accent-dim: #4a9d63;
      --farm-muted: #8b9aab;
    }
    .farm-stats {
      font-family: "DM Sans", system-ui, sans-serif;
      background: var(--farm-bg);
      color: #e6edf3;
      min-height: 100vh;
    }
    .farm-stats__hero {
      background: linear-gradient(165deg, var(--farm-surface) 0%, var(--farm-bg) 55%);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--farm-border);
      padding: 2.5rem 0 2rem;
    }
    .farm-stats__hero h1 {
      font-family: "Instrument Serif", Georgia, serif;
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 2.75rem);
      font-weight: 400;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
      margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
      color: #f0f4f8;
    }
    .farm-stats__hero p.lead {
      color: var(--farm-muted);
      max-width: 44rem;
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 1.05rem;
    }
    .farm-stats__badge {
      display: inline-block;
      font-size: 0.7rem;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.12em;
      color: var(--farm-accent);
      border: 1px solid var(--farm-border);
      padding: 0.2rem 0.55rem;
      border-radius: 999px;
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }
    .stat-card {
      background: var(--farm-surface);
      border: 1px solid var(--farm-border);
      border-radius: 0.5rem;
      padding: 1.1rem 1.2rem;
      height: 100%;
    }
    .stat-card__label {
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.06em;
      color: var(--farm-muted);
      margin-bottom: 0.35rem;
    }
    .stat-card__value {
      font-size: 1.45rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #f0f4f8;
      font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;
    }
    .farm-stats h2 {
      font-family: "Instrument Serif", Georgia, serif;
      font-size: 1.65rem;
      font-weight: 400;
      margin: 2.5rem 0 1rem;
      color: #f0f4f8;
    }
    .farm-stats table {
      width: 100%;
      font-size: 0.875rem;
      border-collapse: collapse;
    }
    .farm-stats table th,
    .farm-stats table td {
      padding: 0.55rem 0.65rem;
      text-align: left;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--farm-border);
    }
    .farm-stats table th {
      color: var(--farm-muted);
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    }
    .farm-stats table td.num {
      font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;
      text-align: right;
    }
    .farm-stats .callout {
      background: var(--farm-surface);
      border: 1px solid var(--farm-border);
      border-radius: 0.5rem;
      padding: 1rem 1.15rem;
      margin: 1.5rem 0 0;
      color: var(--farm-muted);
      font-size: 0.9rem;
    }
    .farm-stats footer {
      border-top: 1px solid var(--farm-border);
      padding: 2rem 0;
      margin-top: 3rem;
      color: var(--farm-muted);
      font-size: 0.85rem;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body class="farm-stats">
  <header class="farm-stats__hero">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="farm-stats__badge">Community</span>
      <h1>Farm statistics</h1>
      <p class="lead">Economy-wide totals from the Discord farming minigame, plus top farmers by balance and farm XP. <a href="{{ publicBaseUrl }}/docs/farm" class="link-success">Player guide</a></p>
      <p class="lead mt-2 mb-0"><small class="text-body-secondary">Canonical: <a href="{{ publicBaseUrl }}/stats/farm" class="link-success">{{ publicBaseUrl }}/stats/farm</a></small></p>
    </div>
  </header>

  <div class="container py-4">
    <p class="text-body-secondary mb-3">Farmers with a profile: <strong class="text-body">{{ farmerCountLabel }}</strong></p>

    <div class="row g-3">
      <div class="col-sm-6 col-lg-4">
        <div class="stat-card">
          <div class="stat-card__label">Crop units harvested</div>
          <div class="stat-card__value">{{ globalStats.totalHarvest }}</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-sm-6 col-lg-4">
        <div class="stat-card">
          <div class="stat-card__label">Plant actions</div>
          <div class="stat-card__value">{{ globalStats.totalPlant }}</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-sm-6 col-lg-4">
        <div class="stat-card">
          <div class="stat-card__label">Land expansions</div>
          <div class="stat-card__value">{{ globalStats.landExpansions }}</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-sm-6 col-lg-4">
        <div class="stat-card">
          <div class="stat-card__label">Shop seed units bought</div>
          <div class="stat-card__value">{{ globalStats.shopBought }}</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-sm-6 col-lg-4">
        <div class="stat-card">
          <div class="stat-card__label">Seed units bought while planting</div>
          <div class="stat-card__value">{{ globalStats.plantBought }}</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-sm-6 col-lg-4">
        <div class="stat-card">
          <div class="stat-card__label">Crop units sold</div>
          <div class="stat-card__value">{{ globalStats.totalSold }}</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="callout">
      Harvest, plant count, and land expansions include history backfilled from farm XP logs where possible.
      Shop purchases, seeds bought at plant time, and crop units sold are counted from when this tracking went live — older activity is not included in those three figures.
    </div>

    <h2>Top farmers by balance</h2>
    <div class="table-responsive">
      <table>
        <thead>
          <tr>
            <th>#</th>
            <th>Farmer</th>
            <th class="num">Balance</th>
            <th class="num">Farm XP</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          {% for row in topMoney %}
          <tr>
            <td>{{ row.rank }}</td>
            <td>{{ row.displayName }}</td>
            <td class="num">${{ row.moneyLabel }}</td>
            <td class="num">{{ row.farmXpLabel }}</td>
          </tr>
          {% endfor %}
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>

    <h2>Top farmers by farm XP</h2>
    <div class="table-responsive">
      <table>
        <thead>
          <tr>
            <th>#</th>
            <th>Farmer</th>
            <th class="num">Farm XP</th>
            <th class="num">Balance</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          {% for row in topFarmXp %}
          <tr>
            <td>{{ row.rank }}</td>
            <td>{{ row.displayName }}</td>
            <td class="num">{{ row.farmXpLabel }}</td>
            <td class="num">${{ row.moneyLabel }}</td>
          </tr>
          {% endfor %}
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>

    <footer>
      <div class="container">
        <p class="mb-0">&copy; {{ docYear }} · Names shown when the bot has a matching web login record; otherwise a short anonymous label is used.</p>
      </div>
    </footer>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
